 Continuous learning self.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       本課程首先介紹：熱力關係、多相與多成分系統、化學平衡與熱力設計，最後闡述統計熱力學觀點與熵之詮釋。This course introduces thermodynamic relations, multi-phase and multi-component systems, chemical balance and thermal design, and finally elaborate interpretation of statistical thermodynamics and entropy of view.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
熱力關係多相與多成分系統化學平衡與熱力設計統計熱力學觀點與熵之詮釋 

